<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://truthout.org/video/david-harvey-and-gar-alperovitz-on-cooperation-and-capitalism/">Gar Alperovitz and David Harvey on "Cooperation and Capitalism"</a></li>
</ul>
